    <section id="service"><h2>1. The service</h2><p>SourcemAI provides an AI Sales Intelligence Layer that monitors third-party signals (public funding events, job postings, CRM activity, and similar open signals) and surfaces ranked account recommendations to your sales team via a daily mobile digest and web dashboard.</p></section>
    <section id="accounts"><h2>2. Accounts &amp; acceptable use</h2><p>You agree to provide accurate account information, to keep your credentials secure, and to use SourcemAI only for your own sales operations. You will not reverse-engineer the service, scrape at unreasonable rates, or upload data you don't have the right to process.</p></section>
    <section id="billing"><h2>3. Billing, plans, and cancellation</h2><p>SourcemAI ships in two tiers: <strong>Solidify</strong> at <strong>$1,599/year</strong> per organization, and <strong>Execute</strong> at <strong>$109/year</strong> per seat, billed annually. The Solidify tier includes a 14-day trial with no card required. Execution starts when you add seats. Cancellations take effect at the end of the current billing period and you'll retain access until then.</p></section>
    <section id="data"><h2>4. Your data and privacy</h2><p>Data you upload or sync (accounts, contacts, CRM tokens) is processed only to surface the digest and is encrypted at rest. See our <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a> and <a href="/dpa">Data Processing Addendum</a> for details, including GDPR rights.</p></section>
    <section id="termination"><h2>5. Termination</h2><p>Either party can terminate at any time. We may suspend accounts that violate these terms. You can export your data at any time via the GDPR export endpoint.</p></section>
    <section id="liability"><h2>6. Liability</h2><p>To the maximum extent permitted by law, our aggregate liability is limited to fees paid in the last 12 months. We do not guarantee the accuracy of any third-party signal source.</p></section>
    <section id="changes"><h2>7. Changes to these terms</h2><p>We'll notify active customers by email at least 30 days before material changes take effect.</p></section>
